#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">银监会后妈：尤其是不能跟你“银行哥哥”抢生意。你就放点高风险的小额信贷就得了。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">P2P</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">儿子：妈，我跟“银行哥哥”比也没啥优势啊，“银行哥哥”放大额其实成本很低的啊。我抢不了他们的生意的啊。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-hei