; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">如果单纯是这些也就算了，这淫贱会（不好意思手误），这银监会后妈觉得这些还不够，再给你来个第三章第十条第三小条</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://imgmywdzj.wdzj.com/group1/M00/05/0A/Ci5Kg1e-4c6AMUdQAAAS1iXm_CQ464.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"zoom\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 850px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">银监会后妈：儿子啊，你看妈对你多好。原来你嫖完啊，不是，又手误了。是骗完，你得给人家钱。现在就好了，你干完提裤子就能走，怎么样，妈对你好不？</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">P2P</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">儿子：妈，人家出来卖也是要养家的啊。我在之前试过了，不给钱都不让干啊。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">银监会后妈：你那时候太早了，现在不一样了啊。现在这社交多发达，陌陌啊，探探啊，碰碰啊，抱抱啊啥的，你约啊</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">~~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">P2P</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">儿子：我。。。。。。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">银监会后妈：还有儿子，你可不能跟他们打感情牌哦，你得明明白白告诉他们，你就是跟他们约炮。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://imgmywdzj.wdzj.com/group1/M00/15/2F/Ci8yele-4eaAMXhtAAAc9onrY4g323.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"zoom\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 850px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">P2P</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">儿子：妈，这概率也太低了，我长的又没有我哥他们帅，很难约啊。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">银监会后妈：虽然不能打感情牌，但是你可以教育他们啊，你跟他们说约炮虽然有风险但是同样也是很爽的行为啊。你要想办法改变他们，去给他们洗脑。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">P2P</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">儿子：妈，我（收益）小啊。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">银监会后妈：你看你股票哥哥，那多小啊（熊市的时候）。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">P2P</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">儿子：妈，那是我哥没勃起，牛起来（牛市），那（收益）很大的啊！</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">银监会后妈：你要对自己有信心啊，你哥平均</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">9</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">年才勃起一次（政府换届平稳后一般会有牛市）啊。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">P2P</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">儿子：。。。。。。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">P2P</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">儿子：妈，你看我积极学习外国知识，运用最先进的互联网技术，努力为那些资质很低的投资人谋取性福，我这么努力，你不能因为一点错误就这么对我啊（委屈脸）。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">银监会后妈：你啊，就是你哥哥姐姐的补充（网贷定位还是传统金融的补充）。不过你也不用立刻改你的那些毛病，我给你</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">12</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">个月时间呢。乖哈</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">~~</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">回去改</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">~~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">P2P</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">儿子：妈，我不是亲生的吧？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">最后，我只能说</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">这很“银监会”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">这很“既得利益集团”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">这很“国情”。</span></p><div><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></div><p><br/></p>', '2016-09-20 10:21:07', '2016-09-21 18:12:01', null);
INSERT INTO `ad_articles` VALUES ('26', '20', 'App\\Models\\NewModel', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《网络借贷信息中介机构业务活动管理暂行办法》，经国务院批准，银监会、工信部、公安部、国家互信办联合发布，2016-8-17施行。位阶上属于国务院部门规章。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">说明：大型平台自有其“周郎妙计”，无须我等置喙。对中小平台，对投资人，有一些建议。因为诚信经营的平台，其利益与投资人一致，因此合在一起说。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一、关于P2P平台的定性<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（一）规定:&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、本办法所称网络借贷是指个体和个体之间通过互联网平台实现的直接借贷。个体包含自然人、法人及其他组织。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、网络借贷信息中介机构是指依法设立，专门从事网络借贷信息中介业务活动的金融信息中介公司。该类机构承担客观、真实、全面、及时进行信息披露的责任，不承担借贷违约风险。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3、借款人与出借人遵循借贷自愿、诚实守信、责任自负、风险自担的原则承担借贷风险。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（二）评析：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">法规明确P2P平台是“网络借贷信息中介机构”。这个行业定位，在社会分工中有无生存下来、发展起来的可能性，有待观察。风险控制是金融的核心部分，自绝于风控的“纯信息中介”，有这么大的真实需求吗，能够养活一个行业吗？风控在金融活动中无可回避，平台不承担，就只能由出借人“自负”，网贷中的出借人有能力“自负风险”吗？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（三）对策：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、规章授予平台的是“不可能享受的权利”。不可公开宣称“不承担借贷违约风险”。相反，“借款人违约，平台垫付本息”是必选动作。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">平台要主动承担风控义务，这是平台的核心竞争力。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、平台老板可以考虑签署最高额保证合同。这或许不能为平台增信，但至少表明平台的意愿。平台也可以与担保公司合作，明显地，这会增加成本。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3、投资人对宣称“不承担借贷违约风险”的平台，要决绝离去。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">二、备案管理<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（一）规定</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、向工商登记注册地地方金融监管部门备案登记。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">地方金融监管部门应当在各省（区、市）规定的时限内完成备案登记手续。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">备案登记不构成对网络借贷信息中介机构经营能力、合规程度、资信状况的认可和评价。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">地方金融监管部门有权对备案登记后的网络借贷信息中介机构进行评估分类，并在官方网站上公示。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、按照通信主管部门的相关规定，申请相应的电信业务经营许可；未按规定申请电信业务经营许可的，不得开展网络借贷信息中介业务。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 14pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">工商登记 → 地方金融监管部门备案登记 → 电信业务经营许可。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">备案管理虽是后置程序，却是开展业务的必备条件。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（二）评析</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 备案管理是政府对特种行业的通行监管措施，无可非议。从条文看，备案登记只进行形式审查；ICP证发放要进行实质审查。因此，监管实践的松紧度才是最需观察的因素。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">ICP证是平台的生死牌。政策的真实动机、底线及灵活性体现在三方面：颁发ICP证的实际标准；对“无证经营”的执法力度；政策本身是否调整。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">(三)对策</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">时限规定是针对新设机构的。对于存量平台而言，有12个月整改期，这段“整改期”其实也是政策反响的观察期；各地有权出台实施办法，监管尺度肯定松紧不一。因此，平台完全可以观望一下。平台是一个市场主体，监管属于外生成本，如果申请ICP证成本过高，上赶着申请无疑“找死”。只要不侵害投资人利益，“未持证”不等同于政府重点打击的“违法犯罪行为”。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">三、平台的义务<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《暂行办法》第九条。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 该条规定了平台的十项义务，有些是业务流程概述，有些是行政法义务，有些是民法（侵权行为法）义务。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 与投资人关系密切的是第（六）、（九）项，“妥善保管出借人与借款人的资料和交易信息，不得删除、篡改，不得非法买卖、泄露出借人与借款人的基本信息和交易信息”、“按照相关要求做好互联网信息内容管理、网络与信息安全相关工作”。平台违反客户信息、交易信息保护及系统安全义务，给出借人、借款人造成损害的，要承担侵权责任；构成犯罪的，要承担刑事责任。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">四、负面行为清单<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">（一）规定</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27.55pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">《暂行办法》第十条，十三项禁令。</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（二）评析</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这条禁令，从政策目标分为两类：一类是对平台经营行为的规范（矫正），包括第一、二、三、四、六、十、十一项；一类是对平台经营范围（资质）的限制，包括第五、七、八、九、十二项。第十三项属于兜底性规定。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从投资人角度，分为三类。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、既是政策红线，又是投资人考察、评估、监督平台时必须坚守底线的行为，合计四项。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（一）为自身或变相为自身融资；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（六）将融资项目的期限进行拆分；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（十）虚构、夸大融资项目的真实性、收益前景，隐瞒融资项目的瑕疵及风险，以歧义性语言或其他欺骗性手段等进行虚假片面宣传或促销等，捏造、散布虚假信息或不完整信息损害他人商业信誉，误导出借人或借款人；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（十一）向借款用途为投资股票、场外配资、期货合约、结构化产品及其他衍生品等高风险的融资提供信息中介服务；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">自融、拆标、虚假宣传、高风险借款人四种情况，是行业公认的高危行为。其危险性仅次于假标、侵占、挥霍、跑路等违法犯罪行为。&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">关于自融（平台吸收投资人资金用于自身及关联企业）：①、法律上属于典型的非法吸收公众存款；②、只要是卷入自融的老板，其资金链必定是极度紧张，自融无异于饮鸩止渴；③、自融平台，通常有着“极佳的客户体验”，而且从无“逾期”，欺骗性很大。但是，它风险集中，一旦爆雷，就片甲无存，多少“著名”平台因自融灰飞烟灭。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、投资人可以容许平台依规整改的行为，合计七项。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（二）直接或间接接受、归集出借人的资金；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（四）自行或委托、授权第三方在互联网、固定电话、移动电话等电子渠道以外的物理场所进行宣传或推介融资项目；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（五）发放贷款，但法律法规另有规定的除外；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（七）自行发售理财等金融产品募集资金，代销银行理财、券商资管、基金、保险或信托产品等金融产品；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（八）开展类资产证券化业务或实现以打包资产、证券化资产、信托资产、基金份额等形式的债权转让行为；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（九）除法律法规和网络借贷有关监管规定允许外，与其他机构投资、代理销售、经纪等业务进行任何形式的混合、捆绑、代理；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（十二）从事股权众筹等业务；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">设立资金池，明显违规，为不良平台自融、挪用甚至跑路开了方便之门；但作为行业潜规则，存在即有其合理性，能够提高撮合效率、缩减交易成本。“发放贷款”，与此类似。线下推广，违规，但不直接影响现有投资人利益。第七、八、九、十二项，超越经营范围，而且使“网络借贷”的简明商业模式复杂化，风险难控，投资人应督促平台整改。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3、投资人可以容许的行为，一项。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（三）直接或变相向出借人提供担保或者承诺保本保息。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此项禁令，是与“信息中介”定位配套，逻辑上是自洽的。但要说它是“保护投资人利益”，未免太牵强，若干评论者穿凿附会，也实在是匪夷所思。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">实际上，如果平台向出借人提供担保或者承诺保本保息，是具有民法效力的。合同法第44条，“依法成立的合同，自成立时生效”。分析此类<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-1475.html\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; border-bottom-width: 1px !important; border-bottom-style: dotted !important; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\">担保合同</a>，其成立要件都是具备的。另一方面，《合同法》第52条规定了无效合同的原因，“有下列情形之一的，合同无效：(一)一方以欺诈、胁迫的手段订立合同，损害国家利益;(二)恶意串通，损害国家、集体或者第三人利益;(三)以合法形式掩盖非法目的;(四)损害社会公共利益;(五)违反法律、行政法规的强制性规定。”其中第（五）项表面上相关。但是，《暂行办法》位阶上属于部门规章，不是行政法规，其禁令不能直接影响民事行为（如合同）的效力。根据《立法法》和司法实践，规章在诉讼中由法院“参照适用”。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">其实，司法实践对这个问题已有明文对策。2015年《最高人民法院关于审理民间借贷案件适用法律若干问题的规定》<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">第</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">22</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">条规定：“</strong>借贷双方通过网络贷款平台形成借贷关系，网络贷款平台的提供者仅提供媒介服务，当事人请求其承担担保责任的，人民法院不予支持。 网络贷款平台的提供者通过网页、广告或者其他媒介明示或者有其他证据证明其为借贷提供担保，出借人请求网络贷款平台的提供者承担担保责任的，人民法院应予支持”。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">五、借款限额<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《暂行办法》第17条。在同一平台借款余额及不同平台借款总余额，自然人的限额20万/100万，法人、其他组织是100万/500万。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">评析：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、对网络借贷进行金额限制是缺乏上位法依据的。<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-1248.html\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; border-bottom-width: 1px !important; border-bottom-style: dotted !important; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\">民间借贷</a>受法律保护，民法通则、合同法及有关司法解释，都没有对民间借贷进行金额限制。网络借贷，无非是借助网络撮合而成，实质还是民间借贷。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《立法法》第80条第2款规定：“部门规章规定的事项应当属于执行法律或者国务院的行政法规、决定、命令的事项。没有法律或者国务院的行政法规、决定、命令的依据，部门规章不得设定减损公民、法人和其他组织权利或者增加其义务的规范，不得增加本部门的权力或者减少本部门的法定职责”。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">请问：对网络借贷限制其金额，依据何在？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、坊间传闻，借款限额规定是为了配合2010年最高人民法院《关于审理<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\">非法集资</span>刑事案件具体应用法律若干问题的解释》。这不成立。①、在网贷中，具备“非法吸收公众存款”条件的，是平台，而不是借款人。借款限额，首先是对借款人行为的限制，但借款人在网络借贷中不具有主导地位，通常不能成为“非吸”行为人；借款限额对平台也构成限制，但显然不能阻止平台“非吸”。因此，借款限额与预防“非吸”没有关联。②、在《解释》中，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\">20</span>万、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\">100</span>万已经是“起刑点”（判断罪与非罪的数量界限）。在《暂行办法》中，借款总余额可以达到<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\">100</span>万、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\">500</span>万。这直接矛盾。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3、借款限额是大平台的特殊烦恼。假设在现代市场经济，政策是一个博弈过程，而不是单向强制过程，那么博弈的结果无非是三种基本状态：政策强力推行、行业整顿；“选择性执法”与行业潜规则相互妥协，人艰不拆；政策调整。不妨观察一下。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">六、银行存管<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（一）规定</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28.1pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">第</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">28</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">条</strong>&nbsp;网络借贷信息中介机构应当实行自身资金与出借人和借款人资金的隔离管理，并选择符合条件的银行业金融机构作为出借人与借款人的资金存管机构。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28.1pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">第</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">35</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">条第</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">款</strong>&nbsp;资金存管机构承担实名开户和履行合同约定及借贷交易指令表面一致性的形式审核责任，但不承担融资项目及借贷交易信息真实性的实质审核责任。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（二）评析</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、资金隔离管理是必要的。但是，限定“银行业金融机构作为资金存管机构”缺乏上位法依据。甚至，涉嫌违反《反垄断法》。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《反垄断法》<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">第</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">37</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">条规定：“</strong>行政机关不得滥用行政权力，制定含有排除、限制竞争内容的规定。”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、《暂行办法》指定“银行业金融机构作为资金存管机构”，“银行业金融机构”就被授予了一定的公共职能，在与平台商业合作中就无权拒绝交易或者漫天要价。对此，银监会应当进一步发布“银行存管业务”规章。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3、银行存管与平台资金安全没有实质联系。资金存管机构“不承担融资项目及借贷交易信息真实性的实质审核责任”。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4、尽管如此，对投资人而言，银行存管对资金安全还是有帮助的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">七、法律责任<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">涉及平台的是第40条。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">评析:</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、“违反法律规定从事非法集资活动或欺诈的，按照相关法律法规和工作机制处理；构成犯罪的，依法追究刑事责任。”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">非法集资，欺诈，这个是高压线。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、违反法律法规和网络借贷有关监管规定，有关法律法规有处罚规定的，适用其规定；有关法律法规未作处罚规定的，工商登记注册地地方金融监管部门可以采取监管谈话、出具警示函、责令改正、通报批评、将其违法违规和不履行公开承诺等情况记入诚信档案并公布等监管措施，以及给予警告、人民币３万元以下罚款和依法可以采取的其他处罚措施。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">八、附则<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 附则对于理解《暂行办法》很重要。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28.1pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">第</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">44</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">条</strong>&nbsp;本办法实施前设立的网络借贷信息中介机构不符合本办法规定的，除违法犯罪行为按照本办法第四十条处理外，由地方金融监管部门要求其整改，整改期不超过12个月。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28.1pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">第</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">45</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">条</strong>&nbsp;省级人民政府可以根据本办法制定实施细则，并报国务院银行业监督管理机构备案。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">九、其他规定<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 《暂行办法》的其他规定，不逐一评析，不是它们不重要，而是因为没有争议。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 27pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">比如《暂行办法》第11-15条规定的出借人、借款人义务。借款人、出借人违反这些义务，通常不会导致行政法责任；但是，平台有权拒绝或者终止服务，当事人有过错、给受害方造成损失的，要承担民事责任。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">比如关于保障信息系统安全稳健运行的详细规定，关于“记录并留存借贷双方上网日志信息，信息交互内容等数据，留存期限为自借贷合同到期起5年”的规定等，都很重要。</p><p><br/></p>', '2016-09-20 10:23:24', '2016-09-21 18:10:35', null);
INSERT INTO `ad_articles` VALUES ('27', '21', 'App\\Models\\NewModel', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为规范网络借贷中介机构经营行为，促进</span><a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-233.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">互联网金融</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">行业有序健康发展，各地金融监管部门正在进行“专项整治自查行动”，由于我国对</span><a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.wdzj.com/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网贷</a><a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.wdzj.com/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">P2P</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">平台的监管采取了两级多部门管理制度，各地监管机构的做法略有不同，我们仅针对共性问题，与</span><a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.wdzj.com/news/hangye/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网贷行业</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从业人员分享，请大家认真积极对待。</span></p><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>　　</strong></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>　　鼓励网贷机构从事三大类领域</strong></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>　　</strong></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　1. 支持对小微企业“贷款”的平台</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　我国对网贷机构的定位是传统机构的有益补充，也就是对银行等金融机构没有服务到位的小微企业进行类金融服务。这里的“小微企业”有具体的标准，那就是：工业企业，年度应纳税所得额不超过30万元，从业人数不超过100人，资产总额不超过3000万元；非工业企业，年度应纳税所得额不超过30万元，从业人数不超过80人，资产总额不超过1000万元。如果P2P平台的服务客户为这个群体，地方监管机构会比较欢迎，甚至鼓励。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　2. 支持三农“贷款”</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　所谓“三农”贷款，就是指涉及农业、农村、农民的贷款。从定义，我们可以看出，三农贷款的外延丰富，这是为了补充农村金融市场。诚然，我国传统银行业在三农领域的发展也值得称赞，但是涉农贷款的<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-672.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">风控</a>问题一直是个难题。飒姐就曾经在山东老家考察过某农业金融项目，我们观察到信贷员不仅要采取通常风控手段，还得深耕在农村，知道农户、养殖户的真实家庭背景和曾经的“癖好”，才能够较为准确地判断其还款意愿和还款来源。浮在表面上的风控，基本是失效的。支持互联网金融企业进入这一领域，可以增加改善农村金融服务的几率，于国于民，都是好事。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　3. 国家重点扶植领域“贷款”</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　国家重点扶植领域包括：智慧能源、协同制造、公共服务、高效物流、便捷交通、绿色生态、人工智能等。这就给<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.wdzj.com/jhzt/ruhexuanzwangdaipingtai/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">网贷平台选择</a>细分垂直领域给出了路线图，对于“物流”行业开展<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-1287.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">供应链金融</a>；对于太阳能、风能等给予支持（由于余额限制，仅能支持其配套企业）；对于生态科技，也可以设置场景提供专业垂直P2P服务，更细致更专业更正能量。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>　　支持网贷机构创新</strong></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　这里的创新主要指两个方面：一是信息技术创新，也就是对于IT技术，包含信息安全技术、大数据分析技术等，鼓励互联网金融企业投入更多互联网研发资金；二是其他创新措施，我们理解就是创新商业模式，网贷行业的主线是居间撮合平台，在撮合平台上开发更多方便<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-3275.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">金融消费者</a>的服务，为其解决争议或提供相应“定制化”保险等，当然，如果<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-3096.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">资产端</a>特别，确实还有其他创新有想象空间。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>　　暂时放松银行存管</strong></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　由于现实困难，银行存管暂不能普及的情况下，某些<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.wdzj.com/dangan/dfjr/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">地方金融</a>办暂时也认可<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-2274.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第三方支付</a>的<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-2081.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">资金存管</a>协议。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>　　自查自纠<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-1259.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">逾期</a>不良</strong></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　对于逾期和不良的定义，目前参照银行标准（详见央行《贷款通则》第34条），对于逾期金额、逾期笔数、逾期率、不良金额、不良笔数、不良率，要求<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://shuju.wdzj.com/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">网贷平台</a>如实申报，并承诺申报情况属实。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>　　结合网贷暂行办法申报涉嫌违规行为</strong></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　8月24日下发的四部委网贷暂行办法，对于网贷平台不能从事的十三项给出了明确规定，各个地方金融监管部门将着重在“<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-1609.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">收益权转让</a>、<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-707.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">债权转让</a>、<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-3194.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">第三方金融</a>产品投资、互联网金融产品发售、<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-2405.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">股权众筹</a>、实物众筹”等方面，要求平台自我申报近3-4年的详尽情况。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>　　摸清借款用途</strong></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　为防止系统性金融风险，对于网贷平台“资金流向”地方监管机关非常关注，除了区分消费性资金需求和<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-831.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">流动性</a>资金需求外，特别提示，资金流向为：房地产配资和校园网贷的，将被重点关注。这点我们要为网贷企业说句话，<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-3288.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">校园贷款</a>引发的恶性事件让人惋惜，但是我们应当区分：网络消费贷款和网络学费贷款，前者因风险较大需限制；后者因支持学生深造具有正面意义，建议保留和鼓励。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>　　关注平台运营健康指数</strong></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　给网贷平台做个“体检”非常有必要，基本指标包括：交易总额、交易总笔数、<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-3041.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">借款人</a>和<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-3042.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">出借人</a>人数、平均借款额度、平均<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-2364.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">借款期限</a>、平均投资额度、平均投资期限、借贷余额、借贷成本、投资回报、<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-57.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">满标</a>用时，十大借款人待还金额占比，关联关系借款余额，存管余额，线下交易总额。其中，关联关系借款余额是为了考察“<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-1280.html\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">自融</a>倾向”，虽暂行办法没有禁止，但要防止被认定为“变相自融”。另外，重视线下交易总额，有还是无，数量多少，暂行办法对于线下物理销售的态度是否定的。同时，请特别注意“借贷成本”，某些网贷平台被诟病的重要原因是苛刻的贷款成本，借款人不堪重负，甚至走向绝路，相关机构已经重视并试图收集第一手资料。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>　　网贷机构本身的情况汇报</strong></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　对于公司名称、注册地、法定代表人、经营范围、员工人数做基本信息收集；对于分支机构，地方金融监管机构悄然把分支机构的调查表也安插进来，就是想侧面再印证网贷平台是否有线下机构；对于公司架构的考察，主要是确定实际控制人到底是谁，顺藤摸瓜发现其是否还有实体企业，是否存在资金输血等问题；对于网站信息，资金存管信息，担保机构，小贷公司的合作信息也属于汇报范围。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simsun, Arial; line-height: 30.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　“行为监管”，已经在路上。P2P行业为先的互联网金融行业必将在阵痛中重生。地方网贷监管考量的维度很多，且有交叉印证，认为自己不属于网贷行业的应当及时向监管机构书面反映，针对不同行业的监管会有不一样的行为边界设定。全国通票和地方粮票，都要在手，才能确保冬季无虞。诸位好运！！</div><p><br/></p>', '2016-09-20 10:49:45', null, null);
INSERT INTO `ad_articles` VALUES ('28', '22', 'App\\Models\\NewModel', '<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;天眼投经历了这多多年的网贷之路。看过太多的起起伏伏。跑路，诈骗，维权，各种声泪 &nbsp; 俱下各种铭心刻骨各种生不如死。骗子平台的狡诈，伪装。投资人的无知，无助。都让我们 &nbsp; 不经要想，这些问题到底出在了哪里？是平台，还是自己，或者是这个市场？</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">当然去找这些原因实际上是根本没有任何意义的，平台倒了就倒了，还能时光倒退不成？显 &nbsp; 然是不可能的，我们也得从中获取经验、教训。是否我们投资之前真的了解过所投资的平 &nbsp; &nbsp; 台，所投资的项目？是否我们对金融有着基本的认识，对风险有着充分的了解？如果没有， &nbsp; 那建议各位投资人好好的静下心来学习学习，我会简单说一下一些基本的排除风险的手段， &nbsp; 目的就是为了帮助大家排除最基本的平台风险。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">工商，平台背景，法人信用</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">可查询地址：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">http://www.<span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 26.4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">tianyancha</span>.com/</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 15.75pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 15.75pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">这一步必须要做，平台的宣传背景一定要查清楚，查明白。如果连背景都要伪造，虚构。那 &nbsp; 还有什么底线呢？法人信用更加不用说，之前如果就有不良记录，按照现在的暂行办法来看 &nbsp; 连最起码许可证都无法获得。因此复制你选择平台，大胆的黏贴吧</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">最近新闻（百度曝光、动态）、信息披露（平台运营报告，项目资料的借款信息等）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;这个很简单百度一下，拿陆金所做例子：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://imgmywdzj.wdzj.com/group1/M00/17/6B/Ci8yelffb8SAEoYHAAKBnA-uTXo087.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 850px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; 仔细看一下相关的负面信息等（当然也不能一味的看到坏的消息就是不好，还要从内容真实 &nbsp; 性来判断）信息披露方面也很简单，看看平台官网的运营报告，标的项目资料信息是否全 &nbsp; &nbsp; 面，真实。例如下面的：</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://imgmywdzj.wdzj.com/group1/M00/07/46/Ci5Kg1ffb8SAEHVHAAChBSN1HXw131.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 850px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">这样做的目的可以排除一些项目虚假的平台，当然一些有做过车贷、房贷的人</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">,</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">判断证书合同什么的有经验的，可以分辨一下是否有造假。下面的我会更加详细的重点介绍一下车贷以及房贷。没有经验的人，建议在后面看仔细一点。这一步只需要看看平台信息披露是否完整、全面就可以了。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">网站办公地址是否与官网照片一致（卫星定位周围环境，可使用百度卫星）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">这个比较简单，百度一下百度地图，输入地址搜索后看街道全景就能确认是否真实。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><img src=\"http://imgmywdzj.wdzj.com/group1/M00/17/6B/Ci8yelffb8SAC_j2AAD9b6DDFJU444.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 850px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">上面的是外景。另外办公环境的话就可以通过百度识图辨别。链接在这里：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">http://image.baidu.com/?fr=shitu</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">高管简介</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">看看平台是否有高管简介，连高管简介都没有的话可能就是都不好意思展示出来。有的话可以看看简介是否牛逼，老板以及高管是否有丰富的行业从业背景。真伪的话很难辨别，唯一的办法可以通过百度识图对比，看看是否是平台直接从网上</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">COPY</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">来的。上面已经有地址可以通过那个查询。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">其他第三方点评（网贷之家，天眼投，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">76676</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">等）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">看看各种第三方点评拿网贷之家做列子好了，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://imgmywdzj.wdzj.com/group1/M00/07/46/Ci5Kg1ffb8WAMtneAACZtxChP50597.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 850px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">就和看淘宝点评一样，好评就不用看了，就看差评，差评里面的内容是否能让你依然不想放弃这个平台（主要看看有没有特别不良的事迹）。当然也不排除恶意差评的，需要各位自己判断啦。个人认为平台的用户体验度还是非常重要的，如果不是背景特别的牛的平台，用户体验再做不好，那还能长长久久吗？</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">车贷与房贷的地域性和真实性审核（如当地房价，车辆价值驾驶证真伪等）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">车贷和房贷是需要考虑其地域性风险的。如前段时间的武汉大水，那么是否那个地区的车贷、房贷项目风险就会增大。还有车贷抵押车辆的本身价值估值是否合理，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat;\">比如看借款人跟车主是否为同一个人，这个可以从身份证和车辆行驶证，以及车辆登记证上看出来。还有就是通过平台公布的信息，车辆登记证，车辆行驶证，车辆评估报告，车辆品牌型号，行驶公里数，以及所对应的图片，只有文字是不行的，这几项是必须有的，如果没有这个平台就有很大的问题，投资的时候就需要谨慎了，通过这几项一方面可以判断平台的风控标准，一方面可以增加平台的造假成本。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">房贷更需要仔细调查当前城市的房价，不同地域的房价还是有很多区别的。试想如果一个三线城市的县城房子，人口每年本身就在不断流失，房子就算抵押给平台变现也会很难。另外的话就是要其产权是否清晰</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat;\">，借款人跟房产所有人是否为同一人或者是否属于小产权房，小产权房的产权证不是由国家房管部门颁发，而是由乡政府或村政府颁发的，这个可以在房产证上看来出来。另外就是抵押物的贬值风险了，由于房贷的借款周期一般都很长，再加上国内房产泡沫严重，要想真正的做到抗风险，房产的抵押率最好不超过</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat;\">60%</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat;\">，这一点可以通过平台公布的资料估算出房产的价格来和平台给的评估报告进行对比，看抵押率是否合理。最后就是项目真实性，判断方法基本跟车贷类似，主要看的资料有借款人身份证，户口本，房产证，房屋评估报告，他项权证或者是抵押受理通知单，有房屋所在地的照片跟室内照片，这些资料都有的话基本上就可以确定项目的真实性。当然最安全的方法还是去房管局查询一下，或者也可以在网上点击省市链接进入到某个城市网站进行查询，这里就需要输入产权人姓名和产权证号才可以</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat;\">(</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat;\">有些地方可以，有些地方就不行，具体要看各个地方的规定</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat;\">)</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-image: none; background-attachment: scroll; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat;\">。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">以上几点都能达到，那么基本就排除了平台的诈骗风险，至少平台所做的都为真实业务。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-indent: -18pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 7.</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">合同的真实性</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">(</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">有无明显</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">PS</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">痕迹，公章辨别等</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">)</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">最后就是判断标的中合同的真实性和有效性，外行人看热闹内行人看门道。我们都是外行人，就仔细看看表面的东西吧。合同看上有没有很假啊，日期签名是否不合理啊等等。想要深入研究，百度一下。有教大家怎么辨别合同的办法。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;8</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">．</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">查询</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">ICP</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 15.75pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">这是链接：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">http://www.miitbeian.gov.cn/publish/query/indexFirst.action</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">。主要看一下是否</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;ICP</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">号证号与官方一致，另外网站负责人姓名与平台管理团队是否相符合，如果不符可以询问平台其原因。另外还有最近新增的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">ICP</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">许可证查询，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">https://tsm.miit.gov.cn/pages/home.aspx</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">官网给到大家</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 15.75pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://imgmywdzj.wdzj.com/group1/M00/17/6B/Ci8yelffb8WAO1E6AAHBzGns7Pk504.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 850px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;\">通过这个地方就可以查询到了。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18pt; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 0cm; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">以上</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">8</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">大要素，大概就是这些了，具体还有什么遗漏的大家可以联系天眼投客服中心客服联系。给我们提供宝贵的排除诈骗平台方案。一般查完这样几个步骤基本就可以排除了诈骗平台了，剩下的是福是祸就看各位自己了。最后在这里说一句，投资都是有风险的。大多数人投资前都没有认真去了解过所投的平台，投资后才想到问东问西，有一个不满意，各种后悔。我想说各位投资前最好认真了解一下所投平台，不要嫌麻烦。毕竟钱是各位辛辛苦苦赚的。不要到最后真的应了那个话“骗子太多，傻子都不够用了”。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2016-09-20 11:04:37', '2016-09-21 18:04:15', null);
INSERT INTO `ad_articles` VALUES ('29', '23', 'App\\Models\\NewModel', '<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">新规出台之后，网贷行业一片哗然，投资人谈“虎”色变，媒体人大肆炒作，我看监管没有把P2P压倒，反倒是让这些手握话语权的人红了一把。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">看到论坛某些大神不实的高谈阔论，楼主心中就来气，本来以为这一亩三分地是净土，到头来百家争鸣也不过是看热闹不嫌事大而已，无论预言“监管把P2P搞死”也好，“P2P将重生也好”，个人也只当是耳旁风。自打入这行以来，听闻的风言风语还少么，最后还不是该怎么投怎么投，留下来的谁没尝过P2P的甜头？！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://imgmywdzj.wdzj.com/group1/M00/07/51/Ci5Kg1fgmzeAO5aVAAD6CHuI3pA722.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"zoom\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 850px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在个人看来，新监管对P2P只是一支转型剂，未来的12个月，大多数平台都会换跑道，转型到监管的框框里，过分夸大后果简直是无稽之谈。依老司机看来，网贷最大的生存压力不在于监管，而在于资金端和资产端压力。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; line-height: 1.65 !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">资金端，获客成本太高，投资者趋利；资产端，优质资产有限，无法满足投资人需求，劣质资产坏账率高，风险又大。这样的两难之境才是其最大压力。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">总而言之，监管还不至于把网贷置于死地，只不过在当下投资情形，投资者需要更严格的考察，楼主分享自己目前的投资策略，希望能给到一点点帮助。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1、不要迷恋背景</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">“背景=兑付实力”完全是瞎扯，你见过哪家平台干爹出来兜底的？所谓的国资、风投、上市名号只不过是为了征信，实际资产端也是普通P2P债权，别忘了宜人贷39.5%的借款利率，同样做的是D类标。最近多家国资炸雷，大背景值得大家深思。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2、募资能力重点考察</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">“资”代表平台“资产端”和“资金端”，平台的发标速度和满标速度折射出一定经营状况，一般来说，发标频率稳定、满标快的平台安全系数高些。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">3、关注投资人活跃度</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">到平台官方渠道关注用户活跃度，如果投资人粘度不高，或多是羊毛党，说明产品本身不具吸引力，长远来看这种平台不宜投。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">4、小而美要看其细分领域</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">除了为数不多的大平台，大多数都是名不见经传的小平台，小平台到底美不美，主要看其业务模式，无论是做哪一类资产或者是理财超市，要看其专业领域挖得深不深。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">5、资产端优劣要重视</strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\">坏账率高低来源于资产质量优劣，从目前来看企业贷坏账风险最高，小额资产类比如消费信贷风险较低，打包分散类精选理财次之，总体资产优劣排序大概是：消费贷&gt;精选理财&gt;车贷&gt;房贷&gt;企业贷。不过，从收益来说，消费贷不如后者。这点大家可以综合考虑。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></p><div><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.65 !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></div><p><br/></p>', '2016-09-20 11:14:24', '2016-09-21 18:01:59', null);
INSERT INTO `ad_articles` VALUES ('30', '24', 'App\\Models\\NewModel', '<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网贷投资获取高收益和高安全是每个投资人的诉求，但是不少投资者既缺乏经验，又无专业知识依据，挑选靠谱平台往往是个难题。编根据投资人需求，专门收集和整理一份挑选平台攻略，在此分享给大家，希望对大家有所帮助。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><img class=\"photo\" src=\"http://imgbbs.ph.126.net/_1y1Rko56-URChoHs9noIA==/6631553749840763977.jpg\" alt=\"6631553749840763977.jpg\" eq=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 850px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>1、考察背景</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">考察背景是选平台的标配，不管是网贷菜鸟还是网贷老手都会去做，但是问题在于如何考察背景？&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一般来说，网贷平台主要分为国资系、上市系、风投系、民营系等，针对干爹背景平台，国资系需要考察国企持股比例，国企背景，平台股东结构；上市系需要考察上市公司持股比例，上市公司背景；风投系需要考察风投出资比例，风投进出时间。具体考察以平台工商注册信息为准。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>2、考察收益</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">想要获得高性价比的理财，就要事先对收益有一定了解。在当下网贷收益环境下，8-10%是中等收益区间，10-13%为中高收益区间，13-15%为高收益区间，15%以上算是逆天高收益。根据不同的风险偏好，可以直接在第三方网贷机构挑选适合自己的高收益，不过提醒大家，在降息大环境下，收益超13%的平台风险比较高，大家要谨慎入手。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/>3、评估期限</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">之所以谈到期限，是因为期限长短可能是安全与否的一个隐性因素。对于大多数投资者而言，长期限意味着变数太多，即便你可能发现平台有不安全因素，但也不能及时撤出。而且，在长期限的捆绑下，资金灵活性降低，很难实现高性价比。在当前的投资环境下，产品期限最好不超过6个月为保险。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4、考察资产配置</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">资产配置是关系平台坏账率高低、安全与否的最关键因素，很多没有专业背景的投资人往往忽略这点。小编举个例子，比如这份中高息平台抽样调查表，收益率、期限一目了然，但是资产类型却不一样，怎么判断呢？&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><img class=\"photo\" src=\"http://imgbbs.ph.126.net/dTp_Jy1qEGuFiRDh5q0cRA==/6631532859119841540.png\" alt=\"6631532859119841540.png\" eq=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 850px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">首先你需要对网贷13种资产有一定了解，如果你有这方面经验，就会明白车贷、精选理财风险相对较低，因为车贷有抵押资产保障，精选理财有强大的资产端支撑，债权更加优质。而风险最大的是企业贷，其次是网贷基金，所以大家在综合考察的时候需要重点关注这点。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">除了这4点基本面考察之外，平时还要多观察平台资金净入、净出量，平台<a id=\"neilianxitong\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.wdzj.com/doc-view-55.html\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; border-bottom-width: 1px !important; border-bottom-style: dotted !important; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\">发标</a>频率，投资人活跃程度，时刻关注平台的风吹草动，才能做到万无一失。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Arial, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: 宋体, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">投资者每一次成功的投资背后，一定是事先做好了100%的考察，无论你是选择什么平台，基本功课不可少，希望大家在入手平台之前全面考察，理性投资</span></p>', '2016-09-20 11:16:45', '2016-09-21 17:59:15', null);
INSERT INTO `ad_articles` VALUES ('31', '6', 'App\\Models\\CategoryModel', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:96px;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; font-size: 13px;\">·&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">天眼盾用户保障计划</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:96px;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; font-size: 13px;\">·&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">问题平台导致平台本金损失最高赔付全部本息。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:7px;margin-bottom:7px;margin-left:96px;margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-family: Symbol; font-size: 13px;\">·&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">协助维权</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">全力帮助用户进行维权，向平台追讨债务</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">赔付规则</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">如果用户通过天眼投进行投资的平台因经营不善导致无法收回全部或部分本金，天眼投将拿出该项目的全部未支付的部分广告费用来作为赔付金，按照每个用户首投部分的待收本金占项目总体待收本金的比例，从该项目总赔付金中，按比例给用户进行赔付。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">天眼盾赔付案例演示</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">小白通过天眼投投资了”XX贷”平台1万元，在没有收回本金的情况下”XX贷”平台突然无法提现，”XX贷”平台通过天眼投为该项目带去的无法收回的首次投资部分总额为20万元，”XX贷”平台剩余推广费未支付部分为10万元，小白的投资占比为20万的5%，那么将获得10万元的5%作为补偿。天眼投补偿小白的费用为5000元。补偿本金的50%</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">天眼投会严加审核本平台在做平台项目：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">天眼投</span>8大严格审核项目</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">1.营业执照</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">2.法人身份真实性</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">3.平台ICP备案</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">4.平台实地考察</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">5.平台担保公司考察</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">6.平台债权考察</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">7.平台背景考察</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">8.平台资金监管考察</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">相信天眼投会给互联网金融带来一片蓝天</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2016-09-20 13:32:11', '2016-09-25 00:55:50', null);
INSERT INTO `ad_articles` VALUES ('32', '25', 'App\\Models\\NewModel', '<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">根据中国银行<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">(601988,</span>股吧<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">)</span>业协会发布的《<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2015</span>中国汽车金融公司行业发展报告》（以下简称“发展报告”）显示，我国汽车金融市场已经进入快速发展期，汽车金融相关业务增速维持在较高水平。《发展报告》称，<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2015</span>年我国汽车金融整体市场规模约在<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">8000-9000</span>亿元，汽车金融整体渗透率增至<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">35%</span>，同比<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2014</span>年的<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">20%</span>增幅超过<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">50%</span>。以发达汽车金融市场超过<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">50%</span>的渗透率为标准的话，我国汽车金融市场仍然拥有较大的发展空间。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">然而伴随着汽车金融的发展，市场竞争也在不断加剧。过去的传统汽车金融市场通常是由商业银行和汽车厂商附属金融机构主导，而后互联网金融崛起，大量的互联网金融机构开始涌入前景广阔的汽车金融领域，包括消费金融、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷、融资租赁等在内的互金机构均选择了不同的汽车金融业务作为入口，正式介入汽车金融领域，国内汽车金融市场也慢慢形成了群雄割据的局面。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">从单一走向多元的汽车金融市场</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">传统汽车金融主要是为经销商提供融资服务、为消费者提供信贷服务，前者包括批发贷款、展厅贷款、零部件贷款、营运设备贷款等融资需求，后者则主要是基于分期购车、以租代购、汽车保险等消费金融需求而产生。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">整体而言，传统汽车金融市场长期呈现单一化特征，而市场表现单一的原因则主要来源于三个方面。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">首先，我国汽车金融公司都是在银监会批准下设立的，因此不得不受限于银监会对汽车金融业务开展作出的相关规定，一定程度上限制了汽车金融公司在业务品种上的创新。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">其次，早期汽车金融市场的融资渠道比较单一，传统汽车金融公司往往只能依赖商业银行贷款来支撑金融业务，然而这种传统渠道恰恰最缺乏效率和活力，在这种固有环境的限制下，整个汽车金融市场都忽略了竞争力及创造力的培养。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">最后，传统汽车金融市场盈利模式单一，即汽车金融公司从银行拆解资金，为经销商及个人供血，赚取中间差价。再加之早期汽车金融渗透率不足，进一步压缩了汽车金融服务的盈利空间，也是汽车金融公司在业务创新上缺乏积极性和主动性的重要原因。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">好在互联网金融发展飞快，并迅速瞄上了汽车金融市场这块巨大的蛋糕，对于传统汽车金融市场来说，互联网的介入除了给原有市场带来冲击以外，更带来了不少突破及创新。经过近几年的发展，我国汽车金融市场也逐渐告别了早期的单一化阶段，迎来了“百花齐放”的新局面。截至目前，互联网<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">+</span>汽车金融已经衍生出了许多创新模式，最常见的包括汽车电商、二手车电商、融资租赁、移动出行、汽车信贷等。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">互联网汽车金融的突飞猛进，一方面是受到了政策的鼓励，<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2015</span>年国家除了鼓励互联网金融创新发展以外，李克强所说“引导融资租赁和金融租赁更好地服务实体经济”，以及购置税减半政策的实行，也都十分利好汽车金融的发展。另一方面则是传统汽车金融在依托互联网进行革新之后，逐渐散发新的生命力。首先，效率的提升。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">传统汽车金融公司的资金多是来自银行，传统金融机构的优势在于利率较低、安全度较高，但也存在着审核速度慢、办理门槛高等不足。而互联网汽车金融则砍掉了资金运输链条中冗长的一环，直接由个人对个人，极大地提升了汽车金融服务的效率。其次，用户体验的提升。传统汽车金融服务是基于线下展开，难以克服空间局限，而互联网汽车金融产业的出现，却能让我们足不出户地接触丰富的汽车金融产品，不仅便捷性更高，选择面也更大了。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">互联网汽车金融也现同质化</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">由于多种互联网<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">+</span>汽车经营模式的崛起，国内汽车金融市场如前文所说呈现出了多元化特征，但事实上，当前互联网汽车金融产业已经出现了明显的同质化现象，汽车金融业务过于集中在汽车抵押<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>融资<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>理财这种单一模式上，汽车后市场生态圈还远未形成。根据亿欧网统计显示，国内发展指数排名靠前的十家汽车金融平台中，超过半数是以“汽车融资租赁”模式为主，即我们常说的车贷业务。即便放大至整个互联网汽车金融领域，车贷也是主流中的主流。零壹研究院数据显示，截至<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2015</span>年年底，<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>行业涉及车贷业务的平台有<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">891</span>家，其中以车贷为主营业务且仍在正常运营的平台大约<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">200</span>家左右；<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2015</span>年全年车贷行业整体交易规模约为<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">580</span>亿元，较<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">2014</span>年增长了<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">28.9%</span>。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">　我们必须认识到的是，随着汽车金融渗透率的逐步提高，社会对汽车资产的认知以及围绕汽车而产生的一系列金融需求也会加速更迭，为此互联网汽车金融行业必须不断开拓新的业务品类，推动互联网与汽车金融进行深度融合，才有可能冲破传统汽车金融的天花板。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">第一，摆脱同质化标签。在过去几年内，车贷领域表现出的巨大前景吸引了许多互联网金融平台扎根驻足，虽然目前车贷市场还未达到明显饱和状态，但整体来看，由于车贷平台数量较多，导致整个车贷行业普遍面临两方面的发展瓶颈。一方面是市场区域的高度重合，部分沿海地区车贷行业逐渐暴漏出疲软之势。不完全统计，广东、浙江、山东、上海等靠海省市已经成为国内车贷平台数量最多的几个城市，车贷平台的高集中度加剧了上述城市车贷市场的竞争。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">为此近几年，包括微贷网、果树财富在内的几家主流车贷平台就表现出了明显的区域下沉趋势，前者基本完成了山东、湖南、安徽、江西等中部省份的全面布局，后者则向武汉、济宁、郑州、临沂等中原二三线城市拓展。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">作为后入者而言，竞争过度充分的沿海地区显然已经不具有优势了，而以河南、河北等省份为代表的中部地区，目前看来还蕴藏着一定的机会。另一方面，车贷行业发展的瓶颈还体现在车贷产品的趋同性上，现阶段车贷行业仍是围绕“融资<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>抵押<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>理财”来发展业务，并未出现实质的创新。随着整个行业竞争的加剧，车贷市场的想象空间正在缩小，因此车贷平台亟需突破现有思维的束缚，摆脱现阶段的“融资<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>抵押<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">-</span>理财”等单一模式，围绕不同应用场景提供消费类金融服务、围绕汽车后市场提供汽车维修、保养、改配、保险等品类进行布局等。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif\">第二，“风口”的重要性。日新月异的互联网时代中，最大的挑战并不来自产品本身，而在于各路玩家是否具备提前站上风口的能力。以车贷为例，近几年<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>车贷行业发展迅猛，甚至被誉为是万亿市场。结合现阶段汽车金融市场发展趋势来看，包括二手车众筹、场景化汽车消费等业务领域也开始崭露锋芒，有望成为汽车金融产业的新风口，有意进入汽车金融市场的平台或能以这几种目前看来仍具创新性的业务作为切入。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2016-09-20 14:45:38', '2016-09-21 17:38:53', null);
INSERT INTO `ad_articles` VALUES ('33', '26', 'App\\Models\\NewModel', '<p>9月20日&nbsp;完成项目功能开发</p><p>9月25日 记事本项目统计还款方式计算功能</p>', '2016-09-20 18:57:44', '2016-09-25 00:53:56', null);
INSERT INTO `ad_articles` VALUES ('34', '27', 'App\\Models\\NewModel', '<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px\">中秋刚刚过完，十一黄金周却已在咫尺间招手，一些人正打算利用闲暇下来的时间选择一家靠谱的<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P网贷</span>平台好好做场投资，但又不知从何入手。实际上这不算难事，俗话说打蛇打七寸，做事抓主要环节，那么选择<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P网贷平台</span>只要紧抓关键点，也是可以将复杂的事情省时省心快捷来办。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px\">随着<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">8</span>月<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">24</span>日，银监会等四部委联合下发《网络借贷信息中介机构业务活动管理暂行办法》<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">(</span>以下简称，《暂行办法》<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">)</span>以来，就此《暂行办法》，业界有 多位专家学者，以及不少媒体人士，分别从各个方面，不同出发点，对其作了解读。尤其对于如何根据该《暂行办法》选择靠谱平台的建议也有不少版本，但终归由 权威官方推出的建议版本几乎没有看到过。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px\">索性，赶在中秋假期来临的这个时候，我们终于听到了来自官方的权威指导发声。近日，江苏省互联网金融协会秘书长、南京财经大学中国区域金融研究中心首席 研究员陆岷峰博士在接受记者采访时表示，监管时代来临，营业执照注册、金融办备案、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">ICP</span>经营许可证、银行资金存管在内的四大证照的获取将是<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷行 业的四道门槛。顺利跨过四道门槛即成佛。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px\">陆岷峰的一番表述，对正苦于在<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷平台选择上不知从何下手的<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷投资者来说，可谓正应景。尽管陆岷峰谈的是整个<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷行业的事情，说的是<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷行业“营业执照注册、金融办备案、<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">ICP</span>经营许可证、银行资金存管”这四道门槛之于行业发展的关键性和重要性，但言外之意，也是在给广大 投资者如何选择靠谱<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷平台递了一句话，即跨国这四道门槛的<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷平台便是成佛平台，基本是可以放心选择的。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px\">《暂行办法》发布后的<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷后监管时代，陆岷峰提出的<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷修“成佛”要过的四大门槛，也是当下<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷投资者选择靠谱平台必看的四大关键项。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 21px;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tahoma, Arial;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);line-height: 32px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 32px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px\">在《暂行办法》发布之前的<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">8</span>月<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">18</span>日，陆岷峰就曾在第二届中国<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">(</span>上海<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">)</span>互联网金融峰会上做演讲时，就已经提出过<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷的“五看五不看”基本原则。并以“互金整治后网贷行业将成为更稀缺的金融资源”来说明网贷行业拥有的广阔前景，以及合规<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷平台的金贵性。而此次，陆岷峰在《暂行办法》发布后，总结出的<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷必过的四道槛，可谓行业内的及时雨，无形中给我国<span style=\"word-wrap: break-word\">P2P</span>网贷行业健康发展按下了快捷键。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '2016-09-21 17:17:08', null, null);
INSERT INTO `ad_articles` VALUES ('35', '9', 'App\\Models\\CategoryModel', '<h1 class=\"page-header\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 20px; font-size: 26px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); padding-bottom: 9px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">销售代表 / 建站顾问　( 长期招贤纳士 )</h1><p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">待遇和晋升，我们知道这是您最关心的，也愿意与您分享更多！</p><div class=\"bs-callout bs-callout-danger\" style=\"padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0px; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 5px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(206, 72, 68); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">【底薪】 ￥2000 - ￥5000<br/>【提成】 10% - 25%<br/>【福利】 交通补助 ( 按天计 ) + 社会保险 + 销售冠军奖<br/>【休假】 周六日双休 + 国家法定节假日休息 + 带薪年假<br/>【支持】 入职后 1 - 2 周的集中培训，由老销售协同商谈客户、交流经验、熟悉流程<br/>【晋升】 销售主管 ( 待遇方面将增加“管理岗位底薪”+“团队提成”)</p></div><p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">职位优势，其实销售并没有那么难！</p><div class=\"bs-callout bs-callout-info\" style=\"padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0px; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 5px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(47, 208, 181); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">【以逸待劳】 这里没有陌生拜访，更没有上门推销。虽然我们很欣赏您自主挖掘客户的能力，但我们为您打造了全面的市场营销，让意向客户主动打电话来找到您！<br/>【鼎力支持】 十年经验的技术大牛，长期稳定的企业合伙人，鼎力支持您的销售工作。技术绝不会成为您签单的障碍！在这里，您可以学到更多的知识！<br/>【出行方便】 公司地址紧邻13号地铁西二旗站A口，出站即到，上班 / 出访客户，都非常方便。</p></div><p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">岗位要求，相对于学历，我们更看重能力和素质！</p><div class=\"bs-callout bs-callout-info\" style=\"padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0px; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 5px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(47, 208, 181); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">【学历】 有互联网销售从业经验的，学历不限。没有相关经验的，要求大专以上学历 + 计算机专业<br/>【交流】 有良好的沟通能力，与来访的意向客户面谈、跟进、促成订单<br/>【文案】 能够撰写符合客户需求的网站建设方案文档 ( 有内部培训、参考文案、技术支持等各种帮助 )<br/>【素质】 有良好的职业素质，对待客户认真负责，有耐心。能够积极地、全身心地投入工作</p></div><p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">走个后门，加入我们！</p><div class=\"bs-callout bs-callout-info\" style=\"padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0px; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 5px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(238, 238, 238) rgb(47, 208, 181); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">【直接负责人】 销售总监：白总监<br/>【负责人手机】 13888888888　( 对于未来的合伙人，我愿意24小时待机静候 )<br/>【合伙人邮箱】 admin@tianyantou.com<br/>【我们的地址】&nbsp;</p></div><p><br/></p>', '2016-09-21 17:21:16', '2016-09-21 17:22:29', null);
INSERT INTO `ad_articles` VALUES ('36', '28', 'App\\Models\\NewModel', '<p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">互联网金融行业渐入健康环境下发展，尽管在监管下不合规的平台&quot;跑路&quot;引起行业负面危机，但优质的互金平台们保持着强势增长，并着眼于互金行业稳定的发展，搭建行业基础建设以实际行动振兴行业。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;\">P2P顺大势 突破两万亿大关</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网贷之家近日发布的数据表示，截止2016年5月底，P2P网贷行业历史累计成交量已经达到20361.35亿元，成功实现了第2个万亿元。</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"https://static.tianyantou.com/uploads/logo/2016-09-21/57e281c534c05.jpg\" width=\"461\" height=\"300\" style=\"width: 461px; height: 300px;\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">更值得一提的是，P2P网贷行业于2015年10月实现了第一个万亿元，用时超过7年之久，而第二个万亿元仅仅用了7个月时间。网贷之家首席研究员、盈灿咨询总经理马骏指出：&quot;这体现了近一年来P2P网贷行业飞速发展的事实&quot;。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">互金已然站在风口处，尽管5月仍有类似e速贷等平台负面曝出，但已然掩盖不住P2P强势增长势头。互金的发展已经从负面的深渊中回归到理性的思考。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">知名经济学家吴晓求大声疾呼：&quot;P2P不要暴力也不能污名&quot;。同时，北京海淀区金融办副主任王鹏也表示：&quot;此次整治不是要清理所有的互联网金融公司，对于不合规平台应该主动合规&quot;。显然，各界都更加理性看待互联网金融行业，并期待行业更健康的发展。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '2016-09-21 20:50:45', '2016-09-21 22:07:41', null);
